title: Abraham-Hicks 1993 AV-7 PARENTING VHS to DVDRip+MP3s v1.1
description:
This is the LAST video tapes recorded in Albuquerque, New NM on May 15th, 1993 (17 years ago)
It was sold only in VHS format. No longer available from AH

NOTE:  The content of this "parenting" video is already included in the other 5 videos.
Since there were many questions on parents and children, AH put them together on this tape calling it "Parenting"
If you downloaded the other 5 of the series the parenting video is already in No 2-3 and 5.



In those days, there were NO INTERNET SITE FOR ABRAHAM-HICKS and the only books published were A NEW BEGINNING I AND II.
No CD's (only cassette tapes were available and this video series)
We had to phone in to place our orders. We were getting news through the QUARTERLY JOURNAL for those who subscribed to it.
Jerry and Esther were mostly traveling by plane from city to city. (no monster bus then)

You can imagine how happy we were when this video came out.
It was like watching Abraham LIVE for the first time.
(Top quality was not an issue then - Third copy of VHS was the best and only format available...but who cares..we had a visual of Abraham in action through Esther.)

To prevent further deterioration, I had my VHS tapes transferred to DVD some 5 years ago. Now for you to enjoy !

There are some minor defect coming from my VHS tapes (which was common in those days) but all and all you get a good sense of how workshops were done in 1993 and what Jerry and Esther looked like in those days.

Thanks to Wally51 for helping me put this together.

A smaller size DVD-Rip of this DVD is coming.  Please check the following website.
